name: Carmella DeCesare
description:
For @ascarsearch2019gmailcom407

Carmella Danielle DeCesare (Garcia) is an American model who was Playmate of the Month April 2003 and Playmate of the Year for 2004. She is also known for her time in WWE as a WWE Diva search contestant. She was featured in the 2008 Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue in the players' wives feature

As with all the Playmate Tis, it skews heavily NSFW, but it can produce SFW images as well

Trained on 1.5 base model but examples are from Analog Madness

If you have any suggestions/criticism/comments or suggestions for the next model, please comment.
